  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/038ad4b855304112bc6eea254904ae27.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/038ad4b855304112bc6eea254904ae27.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In an unexpected journey, after experiencing a traumatic event, a film student finds herself thrown into the world of the dead, a place known as the “Posthumous Lands”, a land created by Alchemy. The problem is... she's still alive! Alongside a talking Crow in a Top Hat and a girl with purple hair, Coralina must solve the riddle that led her to the afterlife and try to return home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/8a7e3efd8756caec3ed49c3f640721cc.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/8a7e3efd8756caec3ed49c3f640721cc.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a curious setting, dialoguing with people who have been dead for a long time, you will travel through the lost lands of Limbo, Purgatory and even Hell. A RETRO adventure with a cinematic experience! Follow the girl who manages to travel through the lost memories of an entire posthumous world that is full of life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/165ee0f59ff12d85396de151392bb73f.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/165ee0f59ff12d85396de151392bb73f.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Coralina: a Memory Tale” is a game about mystery, affection and oneirism, with a diverse range of beautiful visual arts and a relentless soundtrack, which build a plot with personality and love. When you buy the game, you'll enjoy an adventure in retro RPG style, with a cinematic touch, accompanied by an artistic harmony of visuals and sound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/aca1849fd14868653d9f49109af4d998.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/aca1849fd14868653d9f49109af4d998.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/038ad4b855304112bc6eea254904ae27.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/038ad4b855304112bc6eea254904ae27.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In an unexpected journey, after experiencing a traumatic event, a film student finds herself thrown into the world of the dead, a place known as the “Posthumous Lands”, a land created by Alchemy. The problem is... she's still alive! Alongside a talking Crow in a Top Hat and a girl with purple hair, Coralina must solve the riddle that led her to the afterlife and try to return home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/8a7e3efd8756caec3ed49c3f640721cc.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/8a7e3efd8756caec3ed49c3f640721cc.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a curious setting, dialoguing with people who have been dead for a long time, you will travel through the lost lands of Limbo, Purgatory and even Hell. A RETRO adventure with a cinematic experience! Follow the girl who manages to travel through the lost memories of an entire posthumous world that is full of life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/165ee0f59ff12d85396de151392bb73f.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/165ee0f59ff12d85396de151392bb73f.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Coralina: a Memory Tale” is a game about mystery, affection and oneirism, with a diverse range of beautiful visual arts and a relentless soundtrack, which build a plot with personality and love. When you buy the game, you'll enjoy an adventure in retro RPG style, with a cinematic touch, accompanied by an artistic harmony of visuals and sound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras/aca1849fd14868653d9f49109af4d998.avif?t=1772405867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375990/extras_big/aca1849fd14868653d9f49109af4d998.avif?t=1772405867 width=800 height=296 /></span></p>",
